            <div class="problem-content">
                已知二次函数 <strong>y = ax² + bx + c</strong> 的图像经过三个点：<br>
                <strong>点 A(-1, 0)</strong>、<strong>点 B(3, 0)</strong>、<strong>点 C(0, 3)</strong><br><br>
                请根据已知条件：<br>
                ① 求出二次函数的解析式<br>
                ② 确定对称轴方程和顶点坐标<br>
                ③ 判断抛物线的开口方向
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="graph-container">
                <div class="graph-title">📈 函数图像（可拖动顶点）</div>
                <canvas id="canvas" width="500" height="400"></canvas>
                <div class="equation-display">
                    <div class="label">当前解析式</div>
                    <div class="equation" id="equation-text">y = x² - 2x - 3</div>
                </div>
                <div class="info-display">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-label">开口方向</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="direction">向上开口</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-label">对称轴</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="axis">x = 1</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span class="info-label">顶点坐标</span>
                        <span class="info-value" id="vertex">(1, -4)</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

