            <div id="solution-container">
                <div class="solution-step" data-step="1">
                    <span class="step-number">1</span>
                    <span class="step-title">根据已知点列方程组</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        将三个点的坐标代入 y = ax² + bx + c：<br>
                        点 A(-1, 0): a(-1)² + b(-1) + c = 0 → <span class="step-highlight">a - b + c = 0 ①</span><br>
                        点 B(3, 0): a(3)² + b(3) + c = 0 → <span class="step-highlight">9a + 3b + c = 0 ②</span><br>
                        点 C(0, 3): a(0)² + b(0) + c = 3 → <span class="step-highlight">c = 3 ③</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="solution-step" data-step="2">
                    <span class="step-number">2</span>
                    <span class="step-title">解方程组求参数</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        由③得 c = 3，代入①: a - b + 3 = 0 → <span class="step-highlight">a - b = -3 ④</span><br>
                        由③得 c = 3，代入②: 9a + 3b + 3 = 0 → <span class="step-highlight">9a + 3b = -3 → 3a + b = -1 ⑤</span><br>
                        ④ + ⑤: 4a = -4 → <span class="step-highlight">a = -1</span><br>
                        代入④: -1 - b = -3 → <span class="step-highlight">b = 2</span><br>
                        所以解析式为：<span class="step-highlight">y = -x² + 2x + 3</span>
                    </div>
