                        y = -(x² - 2x + 1 - 1) + 3<br>
                        y = -(x - 1)² + 1 + 3<br>
                        <span class="step-highlight">y = -(x - 1)² + 4</span><br><br>
                        因此：<br>
                        对称轴方程：<span class="step-highlight">x = 1</span><br>
                        顶点坐标：<span class="step-highlight">(1, 4)</span><br>
                        由于 a = -1 < 0，抛物线<span class="step-highlight">向下开口</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
